            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>露露檸檬(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:LULU:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/LULU\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">LULU-US</a>)截至台北時間02日01:09股價上漲7.67美元，報160.77美元，漲幅5.01%，成交量1,487,456（股），盤中最高價160.77美元、最低價150.80美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：+0.95%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：+1.22%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：+1.79%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：+3.93%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>露露檸檬(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:LULU:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/LULU\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">LULU-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：-4.88%</li> <li>近 1 月：-17.32%</li> <li>近 3 月：-26.33%</li> <li>近 6 月：-13.95%</li> <li>今年以來：-26.33%</li></ul></section></main>",
